0:00:54.719,0:01:00.719
How did Prajapati remember today?

0:01:00.719,0:01:06.640
I wished that my people

0:01:06.640,0:01:12.960
and my daughter also see who you are.

0:01:15.920,0:01:23.119
Your people believe that
pleasing you is very easy,

0:01:23.119,0:01:28.320
because no rule is compulsory for you

0:01:28.320,0:01:37.200
and no ritual or method
matters in your worship.

0:01:37.200,0:01:42.240
That is why they call you Bholenath.

0:01:44.479,0:01:52.159
Fools do not know that Shiv’s
true nature is the opposite.

0:01:52.159,0:01:59.119
From depriving my father Brahma
of honor and festivals

0:01:59.119,0:02:05.280
to coming to this temple
at this very moment,

0:02:05.280,0:02:11.360
every move of yours is planned.
It smells of conspiracy.

0:02:11.360,0:02:15.360
You are forgetting your limits,
Daksh Prajapati.

0:02:15.360,0:02:24.599
You forget that the one you speak such
harsh words to is Mahadev himself.

0:02:26.000,0:02:27.300
And you are an ordinary

0:02:27.380,0:02:35.080
Not an ordinary. I am Brahma’s son.
I am Brahma’s son.

0:02:36.160,0:02:43.800
If Brahma created this world,
then I am its ruler.

0:02:44.000,0:02:51.760
I made this land fertile.
I arranged it.

0:02:51.760,0:02:56.680
I made it fit for life.

0:02:56.879,0:03:03.760
If I do not regulate my people,
who cares about these Brahmins and sages?

0:03:07.120,0:03:12.959
I am the one
who, performed yagya culture 

0:03:12.959,0:03:20.640
to uplift the whole world.
I am not an ordinary.

0:03:20.640,0:03:24.280
For whom, Daksh?

0:03:25.200,0:03:29.239
For whom did you do all this?

0:03:29.440,0:03:33.159
Running the world,

0:03:33.680,0:03:38.879
establishing rules and
making this land fit to live,

0:03:38.879,0:03:43.720
is the duty of a Prajapati.

0:03:43.760,0:03:50.879
This is why you were born.
So what favor

0:03:50.879,0:03:54.440
and for whom?

0:03:55.840,0:03:59.280
For the people.

0:03:59.920,0:04:03.239
How, Prajapati?

0:04:03.439,0:04:08.879
Look around you.
That sun,

0:04:08.879,0:04:16.000
these trees and plants,
the soil, the wind, even the animals,

0:04:16.000,0:04:21.120
all give their part every day
to keep this creation balanced.

0:04:21.120,0:04:26.880
Have you ever heard any of them
boast of their greatness?

0:04:32.960,0:04:38.080
Son of Brahma, you are wise.

0:04:38.080,0:04:41.080
You are thoughtful.

0:04:41.440,0:04:50.120
You need to look within yourself,
where all answers are found.

0:04:51.750,0:04:57.440
I am a " Renunciate ".

0:04:57.440,0:05:05.600
No love of honor, no fear of insult,
no enemy, no friend,

0:05:05.600,0:05:14.919
no one mine, no one other.
Nothing to take from this world, nothing to give.

0:05:17.440,0:05:21.919
But whenever there is hypocrisy in the name of " Dharm " ( righteousness )

0:05:21.919,0:05:27.840
and it becomes a basis for bias,

0:05:27.840,0:05:34.800
I will surely destroy it.

0:05:34.800,0:05:38.240
Mahadev.
Mahadev.

0:07:03.540,0:07:13.680
I told you.
One day Sati will surely

0:07:13.680,0:07:19.199
be cause of Father sorrow. That is why I have always criticized her stubbornness.

0:07:19.199,0:07:24.639
She sees nothing beyond herself.

0:07:24.639,0:07:27.880
" Khyati " sister, its not like that

0:07:27.990,0:07:32.880
It is. Otherwise, before placing the Shivling

0:07:32.880,0:07:35.680
she would have thought of Father’s honor.

0:07:35.680,0:07:39.880
Didi, anyone can make a mistake.

0:07:40.000,0:07:42.960
Going against one’s father

0:07:42.960,0:07:48.880
and causing his insult is not a mistake,
it is a sin, " Aditi ".

0:07:48.880,0:07:56.600
She has become arrogant,
thinking whatever she does is right.

0:08:01.039,0:08:08.919
Didi, please be calm.
Sati is coming here.

0:08:15.759,0:08:20.960
In the pain of remorse
she is burning every moment.

0:08:20.960,0:08:25.240
Please do not say anything to her.

0:08:32.570,0:08:38.399
Father is still angry with me.

0:08:38.570,0:08:40.399
Why?

0:08:40.399,0:08:45.680
He should not be.
After what you did,

0:08:45.680,0:08:52.770
what do you expect? Even after public insult,
will Father embrace you from his heart?

0:08:53.360,0:08:57.519
Sister, what fault is it of hers?
Father himself

0:08:57.519,0:09:03.600
kept Sati unaware of Shiv
and the facts related to him.

0:09:03.600,0:09:08.920
She had never even heard Shiv’s name.

0:09:10.000,0:09:15.440
Whatever I did,
I did for Father’s good.

0:09:15.440,0:09:22.000
The only reason for placing the Shivling
was the idol’s entry into the temple.

0:09:22.000,0:09:25.480
So that no one would point a finger at Father.

0:09:25.600,0:09:33.480
By placing the Shivling there, you yourself raised a finger at Father’s ideology.

0:09:36.800,0:09:41.050
Sati.

0:09:58.720,0:10:02.800
Mother, I need to speak to Father once.

0:10:02.800,0:10:09.799
Take me to him.

0:10:38.640,0:10:41.640
I...

0:10:43.130,0:10:47.760
My intention was not to hurt you.

0:10:47.760,0:10:52.560
Father, I even argued with Rishi Dadhichi

0:10:52.560,0:10:57.240
and thought his words untrue.

0:10:58.240,0:11:04.079
But at that moment in the temple,
I do not know why I felt

0:11:04.079,0:11:10.600
that protecting your honor
was the only option left.

0:11:10.800,0:11:15.040
A daughter could not bear her
father’s helplessness

0:11:15.040,0:11:21.079
and forgot the duty of
being a Prajapati’s daughter.

0:11:24.000,0:11:32.720
But do not punish me with your silence.
Your Sati may live without air, water, or food,

0:11:32.720,0:11:38.079
but without her father’s love and affection

0:11:38.079,0:11:45.920
she cannot live. Give me any punishment,
no matter how harsh.

0:11:45.920,0:12:03.120
But please speak to me once.

0:12:03.120,0:12:10.240
How could you forget
that " Prajapati Daksh’s " prestige

0:12:10.240,0:12:14.760
is not dependent on anyone?

0:12:15.519,0:12:19.959
Certainly not on that Shiv.

0:12:24.000,0:12:29.920
I did not tell you about him because I wanted to keep you away from this dispute.

0:12:29.920,0:12:37.560
I did not want even Shiv’s name
to impure you.

0:12:38.959,0:12:48.519
But you knew me. How did you make such a
big decision on your own?

0:12:50.720,0:12:54.440
I know

0:12:54.959,0:13:02.959
that whatever you did,
you did thinking of my welfare.

0:13:02.959,0:13:10.639
But what was the result?
If I put all the blame on you,

0:13:10.639,0:13:14.920
that would be injustice.

0:13:17.040,0:13:24.399
But to forgive your crime under cover of your intention would not be justice either,

0:13:24.399,0:13:27.399
Sati.

0:13:30.399,0:13:37.040
Sati regrets what she has done.
My lord, please forgive her.

0:13:37.040,0:13:42.160
No, Mother. If I am forgiven,
I will not be freed

0:13:42.160,0:13:49.240
from the burden of my actions.
I want to atone.

0:13:52.560,0:13:58.079
I have considered all the rules you set.

0:13:58.079,0:14:03.199
But no method of atonement is so harsh

0:14:03.199,0:14:07.680
as to fit the crime of causing pain to a father.

0:14:07.680,0:14:12.639
You are right.
You have made a mistake,

0:14:12.639,0:14:16.920
so you must atone.

0:14:24.880,0:14:31.880
For the next seven days,
you will not take solid food.

0:14:39.279,0:14:50.880
You are allowed fruits only.

0:14:51.279,0:14:58.410
And on one thousand lotus flowers,

0:15:05.360,0:15:09.480
you must write Lord Vishnu’s name.

0:15:10.180,0:15:18.560
I promise, Father.

0:15:18.560,0:15:23.040
There is one more rule in this atonement

0:15:23.040,0:15:29.920
which you must follow with full devotion.

0:15:29.920,0:15:36.519
If you fail to follow it,
your atonement will fail.

0:15:37.920,0:15:43.680
Your Sati accepts every test.

0:15:43.680,0:15:47.320
From today on, not even for a moment

0:15:49.199,0:15:53.839
will you let the thought of that Shiv
enter your mind,

0:15:53.839,0:16:00.100
who insulted your father in the assembly.

0:16:00.100,0:16:09.040
You will banish his memory
from your life forever.

0:16:09.040,0:16:16.399
The severity of your punishment

0:16:16.399,0:16:23.420
is proof that your trust in your Sati
has not completely gone.

0:16:16.399,0:16:23.420
I promise, Father.
I will not disappoint you again.